# smart-expense-tracker
A simple expense tracker built using google sheets to automate daily expense entry , financial tracking, data visualization
# Smart Expense Tracker

This project is a simple yet effective personal expense tracking system built using Google Sheets integrated with Google Apps Script. It allows users to record daily expenses, categorize spending, and automatically generate visual charts for better financial analysis.

## Features

- Automated expense entry using Apps Script UI prompts
- Custom Google Sheets menu for easy data entry
- Pie Chart for category-wise spending analysis
- Line Chart for daily expense trends
- Google Sheet sharing for easy access and demonstration

## Technologies Used

- Google Sheets
- Google Apps Script (JavaScript)

